Title: Lt. Jane Doe
Plot: A body of a woman in the Navy uniform is found by two sailors.  Ducky links the murder to an unsolved case from 10 years ago, and the team is searching for the serial killer who leaves the note promising to return.
Writer: Steven Long Mitchell, Craig W. Van Sickle, Donald P
GuestStars: Amy Sloan, Ben Reed, Jack Kehler, David Marciano, Brian Dietzen, Kent Faulcon, Donnie Jeffcoat, Chris Heuisler, Julia Rose
